Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.88,0:00:14.93,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\blur1\pos(453.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.15,0:00:15.74,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.74,0:00:19.27,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies\Nstraight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.27,0:00:22.96,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.96,0:00:26.58,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.58,0:00:30.34,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.34,0:00:33.51,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.88,0:00:36.64,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.64,0:00:40.10,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.18,0:00:44.86,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.86,0:00:48.27,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.27,0:00:50.90,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.99,0:00:54.49,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.66,0:00:59.28,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.28,0:01:02.62,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.24,0:01:11.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi is the Kamen\NRider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:14.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil\NShocker, a secret
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.05,0:01:15.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,organization plotting\Nworld domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.97,0:01:19.43,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to\Nfight Shocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.95,0:01:23.84,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HFCFFFE&\b1\pos(480.495,246.833)}The Shinigami Chameleon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.42,0:01:33.77,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs70\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}Sunada Gallery
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.99,0:01:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Is someone out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.59,0:02:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I don't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.47,0:02:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Who would play such\Na disgusting prank?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.88,0:02:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant Commander Tatsuo Sunada\Nof the former Imperial Japanese Navy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.62,0:02:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there? Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.12,0:02:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Former submarine captain Sunada.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.88,0:02:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish to know the location of the Nazi\Nsecret you buried twenty-six years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.06,0:02:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.36,0:02:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Death itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.24,0:02:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If you value your life,\Nyou'd better talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.17,0:02:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That won't work...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.02,0:02:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.44,0:02:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Show yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.47,0:03:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.57,0:03:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you hide\Nthe Nazi secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.96,0:03:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know...\Nwhat you're talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.14,0:03:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.00,0:03:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker's already\Nrun an investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.97,0:03:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,They know you're the last man\Nalive who knows of the Nazi secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.96,0:03:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better not play\Ndumb, unless you want harm
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.02,0:03:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,to befall your precious\Ndaughter in the hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.74,0:03:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Threaten me all you want...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.25,0:03:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.78,0:03:34.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This monster can hide anywhere by changing\Nits colors to match what's behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.40,0:03:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like someone had\Na good time tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.19,0:03:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not safe...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.85,0:03:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What if he gets hit by a car?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.47,0:03:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.39,0:03:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you get him home instead?\NWe'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.83,0:03:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely you jest!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.13,0:03:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.11,0:03:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, silly?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.00,0:04:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.37,0:04:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What's got two empowered women\Nlike you looking so frightened?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.24,0:04:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,G-G-Ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.20,0:04:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter\Nwith you people?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.99,0:04:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You look like you've\Nseen a ghost...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.30,0:04:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We have!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.67,0:04:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.61,0:04:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,One man... with two shadows!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.82,0:04:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.89,0:04:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.85,0:04:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The sound of someone\Nbeing dragged along.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.62,0:04:50.90,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi had been altered.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.90,0:04:55.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The process gave him hearing many times\Nmore powerful than an ordinary human's.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.40,0:05:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa...\Njust wait a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.60,0:05:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have a great\Npresent for you soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.95,0:05:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I know my fragile constitution\Nputs you through a lot of trouble,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.81,0:05:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,so this is my way to thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.59,0:05:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.23,0:05:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa... what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.53,0:05:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.05,0:05:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.07,0:05:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Awaken, Sunada.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.58,0:05:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.08,0:05:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.25,0:05:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, how long will you keep\Nup that bravado of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.54,0:05:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.56,0:05:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Torture the girl until he talks!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.45,0:06:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.58,0:06:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yumi's...\NYumi's just had surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.07,0:06:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll kill her like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.16,0:06:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, which do you value more?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.27,0:06:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Your daughter's life,\Nor the Nazi secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.83,0:06:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside the model, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.88,0:06:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.03,0:06:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.40,0:06:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been outside\Nlistening this whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.82,0:06:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you're planning,\Nbut I won't let you have this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.70,0:07:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.38,0:07:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.95,0:07:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.63,0:07:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get your father\Nback from those bad men.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.57,0:07:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You will?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.60,0:07:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.28,0:07:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But in the meantime,\Nyou have to work on getting better.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.85,0:07:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a nice guy, mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.24,0:07:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You can borrow that\Nmodel if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.95,0:07:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very important to\NPapa, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.86,0:07:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So it was Shocker?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.27,0:07:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.28,0:07:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But why would they\Nbe after this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.82,0:08:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,A map!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.92,0:08:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the upper\Nbanks of the Tama River.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.43,0:08:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Dam construction.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.39,0:08:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The X on this map...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.78,0:08:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Fire in the hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.93,0:08:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What's a cave doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.92,0:08:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.94,0:08:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks pretty deep...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.02,0:09:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You think there's a\Ntreasure in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.41,0:09:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.76,0:09:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We should probably look into\Nit, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.02,0:09:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.81,0:09:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,A ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.74,0:09:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What's all this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.58,0:09:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,A g-ghost...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.90,0:09:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He's found it, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.54,0:10:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This will save me time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.57,0:10:10.79,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,That Shocker agent before\Nmentioned a Nazi secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.49,0:10:14.26,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,This box has the Nazi\Nsymbol, the Hakenkreuz.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.86,0:10:18.47,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,If Shocker is after it...\Nwhat secret could it hold?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.66,0:10:22.91,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,What is the connection between the\NThird Reich, Nazi Germany, and Shocker?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.10,0:10:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,There they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.56,0:10:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.64,0:10:46.46,Narrator,,0,0,0,,When wind spins the turbine in\Ncyborg Hongo Takeshi's belt,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.46,0:10:48.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,he transforms into\Nthe Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.53,0:11:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.11,0:11:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What meaning does the swastika,\Nthe Hakenkreuz, hold to Shocker?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.69,0:12:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What secret does\Nthat steel box hold?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.17,0:12:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.69,0:12:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He's dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.43,0:12:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I can open\Nthat steel box,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.23,0:12:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,it will surely give me some\Nnew insight into Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.27,0:12:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That Kamen Rider...\NI'll kill him with my own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.23,0:12:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He must have a weak\Npoint somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.28,0:12:35.22,Bumper Episode 2-13,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\pos(355,520)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.04,0:12:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Loyal scientists of Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.26,0:12:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The appearance of the\NKamen Rider has caused
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.19,0:12:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,our world domination\Nplans to fail repeatedly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.62,0:12:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to thoroughly research\Nall of this Kamen Rider's abilities
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.04,0:12:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and discover his weak point.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.64,0:12:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider's power comes from the\Nwindmill dynamo in his belt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.51,0:13:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And the skin on his chest\Nis completely bulletproof.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.27,0:13:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The slits are his radiators.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.27,0:13:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He can jump 15 meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.65,0:13:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,His arms and legs possess\Nincredible destructive power.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.12,0:13:14.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shocker's scientists\Npoured all their efforts
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.54,0:13:18.65,Narrator,,0,0,0,,into discovering the\NKamen Rider's weak point.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.89,0:13:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.49,0:13:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,can be weakened by stopping the\Nspin of his windmill dynamo,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.38,0:13:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,then trapping him in a\Nlocked room one meter square.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.56,0:13:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,A locked room?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.75,0:13:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And that will\Nrender him helpless?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.91,0:13:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.94,0:13:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare the trap at once,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.21,0:13:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,for whenever the\NRider next appears.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.80,0:13:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.51,0:13:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're late!\NWe were worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.15,0:13:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.06,0:14:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.18,0:14:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I was attacked in the dump.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.37,0:14:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So Shocker did\Nmake an appearance?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.89,0:14:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.10,0:14:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears that this box\Nis very important to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.80,0:14:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Tachibana.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.86,0:14:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a tune-up, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.20,0:14:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.77,0:14:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hongo! Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.14,0:14:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to open this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.89,0:14:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.71,0:14:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Abe?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.89,0:14:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Quite a curious box, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.49,0:14:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's made from a special alloy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.04,0:14:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm not sure if I can open\Nit, Hongo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.29,0:14:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This box doesn't have a lid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.40,0:14:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No lid?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.06,0:14:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to find out what's\Ninside, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.55,0:14:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Could I look after\Nit for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.64,0:14:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I might figure something out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.23,0:14:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds great!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.55,0:14:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.95,0:15:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.27,0:15:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't push yourself too\Nhard, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.93,0:15:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.48,0:15:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.20,0:15:11.80,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\bord5\c&HA6CBD2&\3c&H435B56&}Jonan University Biochemistry Laboratory
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.10,0:15:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,After you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.95,0:15:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinohara Hospital, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.96,0:15:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yumi's going to be so thrilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.49,0:15:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.99,0:15:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to surprise Papa\Nwhen he comes home, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.19,0:15:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want her to\Nend up like me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.70,0:15:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,All alone, because of Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.48,0:15:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to crush Shocker...\Nfor Yumi's sake, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.56,0:16:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.89,0:16:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think this\Nis the right way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.03,0:16:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.59,0:16:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.24,0:16:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.29,0:16:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you stopping?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.76,0:16:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.76,0:16:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.18,0:17:05.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The sleeping gas\Nknocked Takeshi out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.36,0:17:09.01,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But his enhanced\Nconstitution grants him
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.01,0:17:12.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,recovery speeds ten times\Nfaster than an ordinary person.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.92,0:17:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.77,0:17:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We've finished\NHongo and the girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.60,0:17:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.52,0:17:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we just need to\Nretrieve the Nazi steel box.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.44,0:17:51.29,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\bord5\c&HA6CBD2&\3c&H435B56&}Jonan University Biochemistry Laboratory
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.28,0:17:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Later than I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.62,0:17:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll save the rest for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.90,0:18:11.34,Sign,,0,0,0,,Testing Room
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.38,0:18:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Heading home, Mr. Abe?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.59,0:18:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Tachibana...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.60,0:18:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Hongo send you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.73,0:18:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,More or less.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.33,0:18:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the box?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.14,0:18:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The testing room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.74,0:18:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I think Hongo's\Ngetting paranoid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.50,0:18:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt anyone's going to\Ncome trying to steal some box.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.82,0:18:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you're right, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.12,0:18:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway,\Nbe careful on your way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.82,0:18:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.61,0:18:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.06,0:18:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But where's Hongo himself?\NHe should be here by now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.24,0:18:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiro, go call him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.70,0:18:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.56,0:18:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you looking so scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.66,0:18:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,A young man like you\Nshould be braver than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.63,0:18:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...\NNow hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.49,0:19:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Gosh, it's dark in here...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.89,0:19:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.07,0:19:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That boss of mine is\Nsuch a slavedriver...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.07,0:19:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It sure creeps me out when\Nit's quiet like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.90,0:19:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.48,0:19:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No one's picking up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.09,0:19:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not picking up, Boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.12,0:19:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounded like Shiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.39,0:19:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are, you monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.21,0:19:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the box.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.55,0:20:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.57,0:20:42.80,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,How far are they going\Ndown the Tomei Expressway?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.16,0:20:46.67,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,I might be able to\Ninfiltrate Shocker HQ.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.77,0:21:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Lake Biwa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.51,0:21:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the Nazi steel\Nbox that Sunada hid.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.47,0:21:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done. So this is the one...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.88,0:21:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring Doctor Heinrich here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.71,0:21:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Heinrich, behold.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.60,0:21:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We have the box you've\Nbeen searching for.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.15,0:21:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.31,0:22:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,With this box, Shocker will take\Ncontrol of the world economy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.75,0:22:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it opened,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.69,0:22:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.89,0:22:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,A device inside the box is constantly\Nemitting a certain wave frequency.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.90,0:22:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If you hit it with waves\Nof the same wavelength,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.98,0:22:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the box will open itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.76,0:22:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You need this device to open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.12,0:22:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.\NI've just received a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.50,0:22:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,An emergency transmission\Nfrom our Tokyo Branch.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.29,0:22:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.31,0:22:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Chameleon Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.18,0:22:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems you've brought us a wonderful\Nprize, in addition to the steel box.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.97,0:22:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.28,0:23:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You sent six men to\NJonan University.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.93,0:23:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But one of them\Nis still in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.53,0:23:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Six minus one is five.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.44,0:23:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,One of your men is an enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.79,0:23:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,An enemy? Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.55,0:23:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.87,0:23:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.42,0:23:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker Leader...\NI will expose you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.05,0:23:31.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi successfully\Ninfiltrated Shocker HQ.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.35,0:23:33.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But a terrible trap awaited him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.94,0:23:36.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider is in peril!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.12,0:23:40.88,Cont,,560,0,140,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.08,0:23:42.97,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs67.5\fnCalibri\pos(499.031,496.481)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.08,0:23:44.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The latest assassin sent by\NShocker HQ to kill our Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.49,0:23:45.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is Chameleon Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.80,0:23:47.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Takeshi continues to fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.24,0:23:48.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What is the Nazi secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.78,0:23:51.46,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And what has happened to the\Nkidnapped Lieutenant Commander Sunada?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.75,0:23:55.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Next week's Kamen Rider\Nmoves from Tokyo to Osaka,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.42,0:23:59.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,in "The Shinigami Chameleon!\NShowdown at the Old World's Fair!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.38,0:24:11.22,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He came here on a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.80,0:24:13.80,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.80,0:24:15.76,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.76,0:24:18.81,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,who sends the\Nvillains scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.44,0:24:21.19,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.19,0:24:23.06,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.06,0:24:24.86,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Start it up! Rev it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.86,0:24:26.19,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Get that engine running!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.65,0:24:28.69,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Give me top speed, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.74,0:24:34.41,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Hit them with\Nall of your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.41,0:24:37.99,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.99,0:24:41.58,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.08,0:24:45.84,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!